Who we are!

Welcome to the SparkE official site. Here we have a list of our sevices, a gallery ranging from faults to new installations and a little bit about us!

What we do!

With over 25 years experience in the construction industry, we specialise in domestic electrical installation and disabled adaptations. A team of fully qualified electricians who excel in getting the job done quickly, safely and above all else completed at an exceptional standard!


A List of our main services include:

  • - Disabled adaptation
  • - Emergency call out (24/7)
  • - New installations
  • - Testing
  • - Rewires
  • - Fault finding
  • - Renovations

Contact us to find out more about SparkE and our full range of services.
